dct_title_s: Map of the borough of Point Pleasant Beach, Ocean County, New Jersey
dct_description_sm: This map is a block print on linen with hand ink and tint. It describes many small property lots along established roads as well as areas with larger swaths of intact land. The map has surface damage and the date and scale were added in pencil.
Source map supplied by New Jersey Department of Environmental Protection
